        "text": "In the Battle-shock step of your opponent’s Command phase, if an enemy unit that is below its Starting Strength is within 12″ of a Chaos Knights model from your army, that enemy unit must take a Battleshock test. For the purposes of this ability, if a unit has a Starting Strength of 1, it is considered to be below its Starting Strength while it has lost one or more wounds. \n\nDesigner’s Note: This means that all enemy units within range of this Aura ability that have lost one or more models must take a Battle-shock test in your opponent’s Command phase, not just those that are Below Half-strength."
      },
