          "Turn": [
            "Yours"
          ]
        },
        "text": "**WHEN**: Your Movement phase or your Charge phase. \n\n**TARGET**: Up to two War Dog models from your army or one Titanic Chaos Knights model from your army. \n\n**EFFECT**: Until the end of the phase, the selected models can move horizontally through models and terrain features as if they were not there."
      },
